<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="reject-vt">reject <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'riːdʒekt/    美 /'riːdʒekt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-accept">1.★ <strong>拒绝；排斥 【反 accept】；抛弃：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>reject an argument / a claim 
拒绝接受论点/要求</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ve been rejected by all the universities I applied to.
所有我申请的大学都没有录取我。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>rejection /rɪ'dʒekʃn/ n   </p></div>